# WordPress DevOps Deployment

## Features

- Dockerized WordPress
- MySQL Container
- Jenkins CI/CD
- Automated Deployment
- Nginx Reverse Proxy
- Backup Automation

## Tech Stack

- Docker
- Docker Compose
- Jenkins
- Nginx
- WordPress
- MySQL
- Linux

